eventRemarks: TS Mar. 2022: This 'station' is what Martin Stein called SINGLETON305. I just changed to name to something more descriptive.
occurrenceRemarks: MKB05: Was not found. Labelled with correct number Mar. 2012. MKB05:The holotype is a male from Kei 73, Sunda Strait, 5,57S;105,57E, 28. July 1928. The paratype a female from Singapore. Type status checked 2003-2011, but may need reconfirmation. DEJ 20200129: Clearly some confusion here. Alcohol lot contains only one specimen, but slides indicate a male holotype and a female paratype.
